name: Storm Clouds
LocationDStext: If you control a related battleground site, your Force drains here are +1 and may not be canceled.  Your Force generation at the related system may not be limited.
LocationLStext: Unless you control a related site, your Force drains here are -1.  For each restricted (•••) TIE present, your total battle destiny here is -1.  (Original concept by Jan Westergard - New Jersey Sta	tes 2008)
